# Global instruction files (CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md / GEMINI.md) are generated and
# owned by the agent harness installer (bin/install-harness.mjs from
# oisin-ee/agent, run by run_after_10-agent-harness.sh) — NOT deployed as static
# chezmoi files. Ignore so chezmoi never manages or clobbers them; otherwise the
# target drifts from chezmoi's stale source every apply and `chezmoi apply` on a
# TTY-less pod fails ("has changed since chezmoi last wrote it?" → exit 1).
.claude/CLAUDE.md
.codex/AGENTS.md
.gemini/GEMINI.md

